BEGIN Step 7 Program

  Function perform_step_seven_prayer()
    - Say the Step Seven Prayer:
      "My Creator,
      I am now willing that you should have all of me, good and bad.
      I pray that you now remove from me every single defect of character
      which stands in the way of my usefulness to you and my fellows.
      Grant me strength, as I go out from here, to do your bidding. Amen."

  PROCEDURE Main
    - IF Step 6 is completed
      - Call perform_step_seven_prayer()
      - Print "Step 7 completed."
    ELSE
      - Print "Complete Step 6 before proceeding to Step 7."

  END PROCEDURE Main

END Step 7 Program
